	* app/drawable_cmds.c
	* tools/pdbgen/pdb/drawable.pdb: The PDB procedures 
	gimp_drawable_is_[layer|channel|channel_mask] were not renamed,
	but changed all over the place. This made the rotate plug-ins
	fail.

