	* plug-ins/autocrop/autocrop.c: Fixed a Bad Bug(TM).

1999-04-08  Michael Natterer  <mitschel@cs.tu-berlin.de>

	* app/airbrush.c
	* app/bezier_select.c
	* app/blend.c
	* app/brightness_contrast.c
	* app/bucket_fill.c
	* app/by_color_select.c
	* app/clone.c
