	"Device Status" dialog, as the number of devices may change
	between sessions

Mon Mar  8 16:45:06 PST 1999 Manish Singh <yosh@gimp.org>

	* Made 1.1.3 release

	* gimprc.5.in: use @GIMP_VERSION@

Mon Mar  8 16:27:25 PST 1999 Manish Singh <yosh@gimp.org>

