Sat Dec 12 17:36:51 GMT 1998  Austin Donnelly  <austin@greenend.org.uk>

	* app/interface.c
	* app/gdisplay.c: tweak to make status bar update correctly (most
 	of the time).  As Sven has already noted, there seems to be a GTK
 	bug involved.

